<div class="box">
<p>
Try playing with the interactive donation calculator to see exactly how many lives you could save if you donated a fraction of your income to the most effective charities.
</p>

<p>
It assumes you will work for 40 years, with a linearly increasing income over the period. The coloured area of the graph represents your lifetime earnings. The red area is the fraction you will donate to charity; the green area is what's left over.
</p>
</div>

